org.hps.conditions.cli

Class AbstractCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.conditions.cli.AbstractCommand
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AddCommand, LoadCommand, PrintCommand, RunSummaryCommand, TagCommand

    abstract class AbstractCommand
extends Object
    This is the API that sub-commands such as 'load' or 'print' must implement in the conditions command line interface.
